From 1ff2e53678a8d55de0ac04ea918b0b1a0b56d323 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 22 May 2026 19:19:23 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Overhaul document library browser UX

- Add collapsible folder tree sidebar with full hierarchy navigation
- Add drag-and-drop upload (drop files anywhere on the browser card)
- Add interactive empty state with Upload/New Folder CTAs instead of silent text
- Add bulk selection with checkboxes and bulk delete action bar
- Add sortable column headers (click to sort asc/desc with visual indicators)
- Restructure layout to flex column so sidebar + main area fill the viewport

https://claude.ai/code/session_012iPFPW34fGnxvg7zhQG5Wn
